txt.en: Several swarms of bees were merely stumbling blocks on the way to collecting their honey. Their sacrifice will be delicious.
Where there is honey there are sure to be bees. In order to collect honey, the bees will need to be removed.
Take care of any bees that get in your way while collecting honey.
